{"tid":1550524,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"偉大的人權領袖 Hong Kong freedoms must be 'guaranteed'","createTime":"2019-09-07T16:25:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T12:04:38.000Z","uid":289846,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"460d8e5e9aa556b1a8e0fc99a464b551781dcd0d","tid":1550524,"uid":289846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:25:29.000Z","msg":"Merkel in Beijing says Hong Kong freedoms must be 'guaranteed'<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7NOVvQG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7NOVvQG.png&h=ce899b51&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nBEIJING: German Chancellor Angela Merkel said on Friday (Sep 6) the rights and freedoms of people in Hong Kong &quot;must be guaranteed&quot;, after meeting with Chinese Premier Li Keqiang in Beijing.<br />\n<br />\nHong Kong has faced months of pro-democracy protests, and ahead of her three-day visit to China this week, demonstrators in the semi-autonomous city appealed to the German chancellor to support them in her meetings with China's leadership.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nRead more at <a href=\"https://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/world/merkel-in-beijing-says-hong-kong-freedoms-must-be--guaranteed--11881002\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.channelnewsasia.com%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fmerkel-in-beijing-says-hong-kong-freedoms-must-be--guaranteed--11881002&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQCwsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=3b92e5c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/world/merkel-in-beijing-says-hong-kong-freedoms-must-be--guaranteed--11881002</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/world/merkel-in-beijing-says-hong-kong-freedoms-must-be--guaranteed--11881002\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.channelnewsasia.com%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fmerkel-in-beijing-says-hong-kong-freedoms-must-be--guaranteed--11881002&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQCwsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=3b92e5c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/world/merkel-in-beijing-says-hong-kong-freedoms-must-be--guaranteed--11881002</a>"},{"pid":"f651dc7a051521a753075d8e4d3e8a4914070c89","tid":1550524,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:26:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d6db93b8c69e74ceda225fb21b3da07f7428f1ab","tid":1550524,"uid":249705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:26:31.000Z","msg":"9月8點應對外國記者+資料整合+3首歌歌詞<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1550402\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1550402</a>"},{"pid":"a2b58c0065773421515a4a4cd87b47e79fcae939","tid":1550524,"uid":289846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:26:53.000Z","msg":"有無旗手下次帶德國國家旗去街術？？"},{"pid":"3ea8167acd7596a6cb24701731f1f51c362cbbb9","tid":1550524,"uid":81424,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:27:32.000Z","msg":"歐盟可唔可以都立香港人權及民主法<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"411f4d3ae44a2e2c815d40293bf0a13482f92a2d","tid":1550524,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:28:01.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">所有集會開始前，應先唱頌或奏《願榮光歸香港》<br />\n<br />\n參加者應當起立，肅立致敬<br />\n右手置於心胸前<br />\n任何非宗教的頭飾應摘除並放置於左肩</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QQQpnEV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQQQpnEV.png&h=d7a5b483&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1898e3329b2a69ddb45fdd60e531294a004a7249","tid":1550524,"uid":289846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:28:30.000Z","msg":"德國總理默克爾即將出訪中國，多間當地傳媒呼籲默克爾就北京鎮壓香港示威，對華表明立場。其中「世界報」集團總主筆的社論最為激進，提出默克爾應該「改訪香港」，當經濟制裁和外交手段都未能緩和局勢，更建議「應該賦予港人難民地位和公民身分」、以及考慮與台灣建交等，向中國施壓。"},{"pid":"c3c8e111f7914048cc50cc749bf4cb9b436b2bd9","tid":1550524,"uid":289846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ea8167acd7596a6cb24701731f1f51c362cbbb9","tid":1550524,"uid":81424,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:27:32.000Z","msg":"歐盟可唔可以都立香港人權及民主法<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:29:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />跟美國機就已經足夠 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b36d5476c95b538437fb80115c1fcfe0ba312587","tid":1550524,"uid":289846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:30:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UuYyhyg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUuYyhyg.jpg&h=316e4afc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"804843e4aa106630046e78047276ad9bfd5b04cf","tid":1550524,"uid":289846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:32:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">除左侵侵 德媽亦好支持香港人權及自由</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請求旗手支持一下德媽</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f3ffa876e8abf46bd7a4c1085a312e8436518f5","tid":1550524,"uid":289846,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:34:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WP82Vk8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWP82Vk8.jpg&h=40c5f16d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"776f00f50ca53c51d0a6429c1e41b42997d5f086","tid":1550524,"uid":289846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:37:30.000Z","msg":"德媽見豬頭新聞仲末出<br />\n唔知係咪令豬頭無法接乎<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">旗手請帶德國國家旗</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01f9f02220a512a2715ef8f22f99fd5762931e9a","tid":1550524,"uid":289846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:39:54.000Z","msg":"香港問題<br />\n但默克爾這次率領大型商業代表團訪華，正值香港社會問題因為&quot;反修例&quot;爆發、數月動亂不止、引起國際社會高度關注之際。<br />\n<br />\n默克爾在與中國總理會晤後說，她表示，1997年中國收回香港主權時香港的權利和自由應該得到保障。<br />\n<br />\n她表示，需要和平解決香港問題，對話是前進的道路。"},{"pid":"fa2bc2ff23927addff7a8ea520e6096b7d49c669","tid":1550524,"uid":289846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:40:15.000Z","msg":"作為中國高層領導，李克強首次就香港問題表態表示，中國政府已經在多種場合都就香港近期出現的問題反覆表明了態度，堅定不移維護&quot;一國兩制&quot;、&quot;港人治港&quot;、&quot;高度自治&quot;，支持特區政府依法止暴制亂，恢復秩序，維護香港的長期繁榮穩定。"},{"pid":"3460f1d85ef3c5b411c77ae6f47c6f52a9e8d321","tid":1550524,"uid":298767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:43:39.000Z","msg":"德媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25df118550362b28bdca88c9426e1cd1f029ea92","tid":1550524,"uid":289846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:44:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eYjajQ0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeYjajQ0.jpg&h=a6c13765&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d06d4c16cc979b3d765e1e5f6968e8f12ff5e3f7","tid":1550524,"uid":289846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3460f1d85ef3c5b411c77ae6f47c6f52a9e8d321","tid":1550524,"uid":298767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:43:39.000Z","msg":"德媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:47:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n國際領袖對香港最好德媽可以係數一數二</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji